Here's one idea.  It simply displays a &quot;show stats&quot; link every time the game goes to a new section. The link embeds the contents of the &quot;Statistics&quot; section.  You need to have the &quot;Stats&quot; passage in every section.

============================
@start Begin

[[]]:
[Show Stats](Stats)

[[Statistics]]:
Score: {score}&lt;br&gt;
Health: {health}&lt;br&gt;
Ammo: {ammo}

[[Begin]]:
@set score = 25
@set health = 100
@set ammo = 237

[[Start the game.]](Section 1)

[[Section 1]]:
This is Section 1 of the game.  Click here to go to [[Section 2]].

[Stats]:
{Statistics}

[[Section 2]]:
This is Section 2.  Click for [[Section 1]].

[Stats]:
{Statistics}
=======================================
